		road less traveled, constantly seeking new horizons in the digital realm and
		beyond. Join her as she continues to explore, inspire, and empower.
	</p>
	<div
		class="infobox"
		style="width: 50vw; border: 2px solid var(--gray-light);"
	>
		<p>Here are a few facts about me:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>My name is {identity.firstName}.</li>
			<li>I live in {identity.country} and I am a {identity.occupation}.</li>
			{
				identity.hobbies.length >= 2 && (
					<li>
						Two of my hobbies are: {identity.hobbies[0]} and{' '}
						{identity.hobbies[1]}
